en_155880_3	In addition, it is confirmed that assailants have got in the Black Maria and committed the murders.
en_155880_4	Police Media Spokesman DIG Priyantha Jayakody told our news team that photographs of the suspects will be released to the media tomorrow.
en_155880_5	Police also said that the mastermind behind the seven murders and other accomplices has already been identified.
